"title": "5879: humiliation",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5879: humiliation",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The act of being put to shame, often in a public manner. Jesus Christ was humiliated through his suffering, degradation and execution. Believers may expect to suffer humiliation on account of their faith.</p>\n<h2>Examples of humiliation</h2>\n<h3>David's men at the hands of Hanun</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:4-2Sam10:5\">2SA 10:4–10:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr19:4-1Chr19:5\">1CH 19:4–19:5</a></p>\n<h3>Michal, by David's dancing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:14\">2SA 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:20-2Sam6:22\">2SA 6:20–6:22</a></p>\n<h3>Joab and his men, by David's seemingly inappropriate mourning</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:5-2Sam19:6\">2SA 19:5–19:6</a></p>\n<h3>Haman, by his death on the gallows prepared for Mordecai</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:11-Esth6:12\">EST 6:11–6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:10\">EST 7:10</a></p>\n<h3>Job</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:5\">JOB 19:5</a></p>\n<h3>Peter, by his denial of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:69-Matt26:75\">MAT 26:69–26:75</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:66-Mark14:72\">MRK 14:66–14:72</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:55-Luke22:62\">LUK 22:55–22:62</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:16-John18:18\">JHN 18:16–18:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:25-John18:27\">JHN 18:25–18:27</a></p>\n<h3>Warnings against presumption</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:7\">PRO 25:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:7-Luke14:11\">LUK 14:7–14:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:12\">1CO 10:12</a></p>\n<h2>People are often humiliated as a punishment for sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:8-Obad1:10\">OBA 1:8–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:28\">2KI 19:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:7\">EZR 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:26\">PSA 35:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:11\">ISA 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:19\">ISA 22:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:11\">ISA 25:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:5\">ISA 26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:9\">JER 15:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:40\">JER 23:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:19\">JER 31:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:16\">JER 49:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:8\">EZK 28:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:9\">MAL 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ suffered humiliation</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's humiliation prophesied in the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:12\">ISA 53:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:6\">ISA 50:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:14\">ISA 52:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:2-Isa53:4\">ISA 53:2–53:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:32-Acts8:33\">ACT 8:32–8:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7-Isa53:8\">ISA 53:7–53:8</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's humiliation in his incarnation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:6-Phil2:8\">PHP 2:6–2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's humilation in his humble birth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:7\">LUK 2:7</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's humiliation through the words of others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:34\">MAT 9:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:19\">MAT 11:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:34\">LUK 7:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:21\">MRK 3:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:20\">JHN 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:16\">JHN 9:16</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's humiliation through the actions of others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:28-Luke4:29\">LUK 4:28–4:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:44-Luke7:46\">LUK 7:44–7:46</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's humiliation at his trials</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:55-Mark14:65\">MRK 14:55–14:65</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:27-Matt27:31\">MAT 27:27–27:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:59-Matt26:68\">MAT 26:59–26:68</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:19-John18:24\">JHN 18:19–18:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:26\">MAT 27:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:15\">MRK 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:25\">LUK 23:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:16\">JHN 19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:16-Mark15:20\">MRK 15:16–15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:1-John19:3\">JHN 19:1–19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:9-Luke23:11\">LUK 23:9–23:11</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's humiliation at his crucifixion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:33-Luke23:43\">LUK 23:33–23:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:13\">GAL 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:23\">DEU 21:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:37\">LUK 22:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:12\">ISA 53:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:33-Matt27:44\">MAT 27:33–27:44</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:22-Mark15:32\">MRK 15:22–15:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:17-John19:24\">JHN 19:17–19:24</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should be prepared to suffer humiliation from unbelievers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">2TI 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11\">MAT 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:17-Matt10:18\">MAT 10:17–10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:20\">JHN 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:2\">JHN 16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:28-Phil1:30\">PHP 1:28–1:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:33-Heb10:34\">HEB 10:33–10:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:19-1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:19–2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are not to humiliate others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:2-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:2–2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:22\">MAT 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:4-Matt7:5\">MAT 7:4–7:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:20-1Cor11:22\">1CO 11:20–11:22</a></p>",
